PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of SHAWN A. MURPHY, Q.C., of Charlottetown, Prince Edward Island, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Bernard Ghert, whose term has expired.
